223
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:50,400
<i>'Saya'                  'Kanemoto'
HIRATA Kaoru        KANEKO Kiyobumi</i>

224
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:53,400
<i> 'Rumi'                           'Kana'
KOBAYASHI Asako      YOSHIMOTO Naoko</i>

225
00:22:53,790 --> 00:23:00,860
~ Dakara sukoshi yume o mi sasete ~
