226
00:22:53,810 --> 00:22:56,410
<i> 'Goro'                      'Chuu'
MATSUO Satoru         FUWA Mansaku</i>

227
00:22:56,910 --> 00:22:58,900
<i>'Komichi'                 'Marilyn'
UNO Shohei            ANDO Tamae</i>

228
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,800
<i>'Kosuzu'             'Hana'
AYATA Toshiki    ASAKURA Aki</i>

229
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:05,810
~ Ashita e mukau tame ~
