MATSUSHIGE Yutaka   YAMANAKA Takashi</i>

232
00:23:05,810 --> 00:23:12,360
~ Waraetara waraetara ~
*We laugh and laugh*

233
00:23:06,900 --> 00:23:10,900
<i>    'Katagiri'
and ODAGIRI Joe</i>

234
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:19,200
~ Bokura warai aeru nara ~
*And smile when we meet*

